bctoolbox
------------------------------------------
Utilities library used by Belledonne Communications softwares like belle-sip,
mediastreamer2 and linphone.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libbctoolbox-devel-5.4.116-1bl1
  libbctoolbox1-5.4.116-1bl1
  libbcunit-devel-5.4.115-1bl1
  libbcunit1-5.4.115-1bl1
  libdecaf0-1.0.2-1bl2
  libgcc1-13.4.0-1
  libiconv2-1.19-2
  libintl8-0.22.5-1
  libssl3-3.5.6-1
  libstdc++6-13.4.0-1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46-1
  cmake-4.2.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  libbcunit-devel-5.4.115-1bl1
  libdecaf-devel-1.0.2-1bl2
  libiconv-devel-1.19-2
  libssl-devel-3.5.6-1
  ninja-1.13.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/BelledonneCommunications/bctoolbox

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/BelledonneCommunications/bctoolbox/archive/refs/tags/5.4.116.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack bctoolbox-5.4.116-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./bctoolbox-5.4.116-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/bctoolbox-5.4.116-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/bctoolbox-5.4.116-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbctoolbox1-5.4.116-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbctoolbox-devel-5.4.116-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

